      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 466.98,
      "end": 467.02,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 467.02,
      "end": 467.1,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 467.1,
      "end": 467.58,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 467.58,
      "end": 468.02,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 468.02,
      "end": 468.1,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 468.1,
      "end": 468.3,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 468.3,
      "end": 468.42,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 468.42,
      "end": 475.14,
      "text": "웨스팅하우스의 설비를 자신의 그 교류 시스템으로 바꿔주는 일을"
    },
    {
      "start": 475.14,
      "end": 476.28,
      "text": "맡게 됐대요."
    },
    {
      "start": 476.68,
      "end": 482.72,
      "text": "근데 이렇게 돈을 많이 벌었는데도 불구하고 테슬라가 되게 가난하게 인생을"
    },
    {
      "start": 482.72,
      "end": 483.5,
      "text": "살게 되잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 483.76,
      "end": 483.92,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 483.92,
      "end": 484.44,
      "text": "왜 그런 거예요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 484.74,
      "end": 487.42,
      "text": "Well, did you see what he was wearing in the movie?"
    },
    {
      "start": 487.42,
      "end": 493.14,
      "text": "He was wearing like 명품, very fancy suits, very nice clothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 493.3,
      "end": 493.52,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 493.62,
      "end": 494.22,
      "text": "In a hotel."
    },
    {
      "start": 494.44,
      "end": 495.56,
      "text": "And he was staying in hotels."
    },
    {
      "start": 495.56,
      "end": 495.96,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 496.06,
      "end": 496.86,
      "text": "Very luxurious."
    },
    {
      "start": 497.04,
      "end": 497.24,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 497.24,
      "end": 498.42,
      "text": "Who pays for the rent?"
    },
    {
      "start": 498.56,
      "end": 503.88,
      "text": "He needed to keep inventing and selling things to pay for the rent and pay for his fancy"
    },
    {
      "start": 503.88,
      "end": 504.34,
      "text": "clothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 504.34,
      "end": 511.86,
      "text": "And unfortunately, he spent a lot of his money and he did not pay his bills."
    },
    {
      "start": 512.04,
      "end": 512.22,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 512.22,
      "end": 513.38,
      "text": "He couldn't pay his bills."
    },
    {
      "start": 513.58,
      "end": 515.56,
      "text": "So he ended up in poverty."
    },
    {
      "start": 515.84,
      "end": 518.04,
      "text": "He ended up in deep poverty."
    },
    {
      "start": 518.3,
      "end": 522.28,
      "text": "And as I mentioned before, he was feeding pigeons in the park."
    },
    {
      "start": 522.28,
      "end": 525.36,
      "text": "Many people thought he was a crazy old man."
    },
    {
      "start": 526.1,
      "end": 531.26,
      "text": "Nobody recognized his genius until much later after his death."
    },
    {
      "start": 531.26,
      "end": 531.62,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 532.42,
      "end": 535.54,
      "text": "그리고 또 하나의 정보에 따르면, 제가 좀 알아봤는데,"
    },
    {
      "start": 536.84,
      "end": 540.14,
      "text": "이 자신만의 시간을 갖는 걸 되게 좋아했대요, 테슬라가."
    },
    {
      "start": 540.34,
      "end": 546.24,
      "text": "그러다가 자기가 여러 가지 발명품을 만들어 놓은 그 실험실에 큰 화재가 났대요."
    },
    {
      "start": 546.34,
      "end": 550.06,
      "text": "근데 보험을 안 들어놔가지고 이게 파산을 하게 되었답니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 550.16,
      "end": 550.94,
      "text": "I went bankrupt."
    },
    {
      "start": 550.94,
      "end": 551.62,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 552.02,
      "end": 553.4,
      "text": "He said the story도 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 553.48,
      "end": 554.62,
      "text": "No fire insurance."
    },
    {
      "start": 554.92,
      "end": 555.84,
      "text": "That's terrible."
    },
    {
      "start": 556.06,
      "end": 556.54,
      "text": "그러게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 556.9,
      "end": 562.64,
      "text": "Well, nowadays, since the 90s, he has become a super popular figure."
    },
    {
      "start": 562.72,
      "end": 563.08,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "start": 563.16,
      "end": 563.54,
      "text": "Tesla."
    },
    {
      "start": 563.88,
      "end": 565.36,
      "text": "It's a household name."
    },
    {
      "start": 565.44,
      "end": 566.78,
      "text": "Everybody knows Tesla."
    },
    {
      "start": 566.9,
      "end": 567.1,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 567.26,
      "end": 570.86,
      "text": "I saw Tesla on the 내부 ring road this morning."
    },
    {
      "start": 570.96,
      "end": 571.72,
      "text": "저도 봤는데."
    },
    {
      "start": 571.78,
      "end": 572.4,
      "text": "내부 순환로?"
    },
    {
      "start": 572.48,
      "end": 572.94,
      "text": "Oh, really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 573.14,
      "end": 574.54,
      "text": "아니, 내부 순환로는 아니었고."
    },
    {
      "start": 574.56,
      "end": 575.32,
      "text": "아, 내부 ring road."
    },
    {
      "start": 575.46,
      "end": 579.08,
      "text": "아무튼 내가 오던 그 길에도 테슬라가 멋지게 가더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 579.08,
      "end": 581.18,
      "text": "그래서 난 테슬라를 생각했죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 582.18,
      "end": 583.46,
      "text": "He's a household name nowadays."
    },
    {
      "start": 584.38,
      "end": 586.54,
      "text": "일단 오늘 내용 듣고 오겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 586.54,
      "end": 592.87,
      "text": "If we cannot reach an agreement today, my company will die right here in your hotel room."
    },
    {
      "start": 593.57,
      "end": 597.07,
      "text": "But if it does perish, so might your dream of harnessing power from Niagara."
    },
    {
      "start": 597.07,
      "end": 599.63,
      "text": "So, do we have a deal?"
    },
    {
      "start": 600.35,
      "end": 601.09,
      "text": "5,000."
    },
    {
      "start": 601.93,
      "end": 602.55,
      "text": "1,000."
    },
    {
      "start": 603.09,
      "end": 606.59,
      "text": "I'll give you 2 dollars and 50 cents per horsepower."
    },
    {
      "start": 607.99,
      "end": 611.29,
      "text": "그 per horsepower, 중요한 말이네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 611.41,
      "end": 612.41,
      "text": "Yeah, horsepower."
    },
    {
      "start": 612.69,
      "end": 613.09,
      "text": "뭘까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 613.63,
      "end": 614.43,
      "text": "마력."
    },
    {
      "start": 614.93,
      "end": 615.55,
      "text": "Oh."
    },
    {
      "start": 615.93,
      "end": 616.57,
      "text": "마력."
    },
    {
      "start": 616.97,
      "end": 618.63,
      "text": "Is that a common word nowadays?"
    },
    {
      "start": 618.63,
      "end": 620.25,
      "text": "요즘은 아니겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 620.79,
      "end": 623.41,
      "text": "자, 어떤 내용인지 너무너무 궁금한데."
    },
    {
      "start": 624.25,
      "end": 628.51,
      "text": "지금 테슬라가 made a very tempting offer."
    },
    {
      "start": 628.79,
      "end": 630.61,
      "text": "아주 솔깃한 그런 제안을 해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 632.07,
      "end": 635.67,
      "text": "에디슨의 3분의 1 정도 되는 그 단가로"
    },
    {
      "start": 635.67,
      "end": 639.73,
      "text": "자기의 그 발명품을 운용할 수 있다라고 하면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.73,
      "end": 641.89,
      "text": "투자하라라고 이야기를 하거든요."
    },
    {
      "start": 642.41,
      "end": 644.93,
      "text": "So, after all, they decided to work together, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 644.93,
      "end": 648.35,
      "text": "Yes, they are partners now, business partners."
    },
    {
      "start": 649.55,
      "end": 652.19,
      "text": "And they decided to work together to build."
    },
    {
      "start": 652.59,
      "end": 655.55,
      "text": "The thing they need to build the most is an AC motor"
    },
    {
      "start": 655.55,
      "end": 659.49,
      "text": "that can work practically to provide electricity"
    },
    {
      "start": 659.49,
      "end": 662.17,
      "text": "long distance across the country."
    },
    {
      "start": 662.73,
      "end": 665.25,
      "text": "So, Westinghouse does not have the ability to develop that."
    },
    {
      "start": 665.53,
      "end": 666.73,
      "text": "He needs 테슬라 skills."
    },
    {
      "start": 666.79,
      "end": 667.07,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 667.45,
      "end": 669.93,
      "text": "그래서 이제 둘이 딱 합치게 되니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 669.93,
      "end": 672.81,
      "text": "뭐 무서울 게 없을 것 같은데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 672.95,
      "end": 673.11,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 673.11,
      "end": 676.95,
      "text": "테슬라 must have been so happy to invent as much as he could."
    },
    {
      "start": 677.31,
      "end": 677.45,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 677.89,
      "end": 679.29,
      "text": "이제 웨스팅하우스를 만나가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 679.29,
      "end": 683.43,
      "text": "자기가 하고 싶은 모든 발명품들을 만들어낼 수 있었을 겁니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 683.47,
      "end": 683.85,
      "text": "Freedom!"
    },
    {
      "start": 684.81,
      "end": 688.59,
      "text": "He doesn't have to have a guy looking over his shoulder all the time"
    },
    {
      "start": 688.59,
      "end": 690.25,
      "text": "and being critical."
    },
    {
      "start": 690.49,
      "end": 691.31,
      "text": "그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 691.87,
      "end": 693.99,
      "text": "자, 일단 주요 표현들 살펴볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 694.57,
      "end": 695.85,
      "text": "Reach an agreement."
    },
    {
      "start": 696.27,
      "end": 700.25,
      "text": "Reach an agreement라는 동사 구조를 들으실 텐데"
    },
    {
      "start": 700.25,
      "end": 702.39,
      "text": "reach가 뭐예요? 도달하는 거죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 702.39,
      "end": 702.89,
      "text": "Reach"
    },
    {
      "start": 702.89,
      "end": 707.73,
      "text": "An agreement라고 해서 합의에 도달하다라는 의미입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 707.79,
      "end": 708.77,
      "text": "We reached an agreement."
    },
    {
      "start": 709.13,
      "end": 710.91,
      "text": "I signed the paper."
    },
    {
      "start": 712.31,
      "end": 712.95,
      "text": "Have a deal."
    },
    {
      "start": 713.29,
      "end": 714.13,
      "text": "Very similar."
    },
    {
      "start": 714.41,
      "end": 714.65,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 715.15,
      "end": 716.33,
      "text": "비슷한 의미였어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 716.53,
      "end": 718.93,
      "text": "Reach an agreement하고 have a deal."
    },
    {
      "start": 719.43,
      "end": 720.69,
      "text": "의미가 좀 비슷하네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 720.75,
      "end": 722.67,
      "text": "Have a deal 어떻게 자주 쓰는지."
    },
    {
      "start": 722.67,
      "end": 724.35,
      "text": "Do we have a deal?"
    },
    {
      "start": 724.35,
      "end": 726.79,
      "text": "아, 우리 거래가 성사된 건가?"
    },
    {
      "start": 727.13,
      "end": 727.61,
      "text": "이런 의미."
    },
    {
      "start": 728.07,
      "end": 729.05,
      "text": "거래를 하다."
    },
    {
      "start": 729.23,
      "end": 729.81,
      "text": "Have a deal."
    },
    {
      "start": 730.75,
      "end": 732.23,
      "text": "Per horsepower."
    },
    {
      "start": 732.63,
      "end": 732.93,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 733.47,
      "end": 735.01,
      "text": "Per이라는 P-E-R."
    },
    {
      "start": 735.15,
      "end": 738.03,
      "text": "이게 당위당이라고 생각하면 되잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 738.55,
      "end": 739.53,
      "text": "단위당."
    },
    {
      "start": 740.37,
      "end": 742.59,
      "text": "그래서 per horsepower이라고 했으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 742.59,
      "end": 744.03,
      "text": "마력당."
    },
    {
      "start": 744.03,
      "end": 747.05,
      "text": "발음이 굉장히 정확합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 747.21,
      "end": 747.57,
      "text": "마력당."
    },
    {
      "start": 747.93,
      "end": 748.37,
      "text": "마력당."
    },
    {
      "start": 748.37,
      "end": 748.81,
      "text": "마력당."
    },
    {
      "start": 750.13,
      "end": 750.83,
      "text": "아, 마."
    },
    {
      "start": 751.05,
      "end": 751.79,
      "text": "horse, 마."
    },
    {
      "start": 751.91,
      "end": 752.05,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 752.21,
      "end": 753.05,
      "text": "마력당."
    },
    {
      "start": 753.35,
      "end": 753.45,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 753.77,
      "end": 754.81,
      "text": "per horsepower."
    },
    {
      "start": 754.99,
      "end": 755.13,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 755.21,
      "end": 757.17,
      "text": "정확한 발음으로 이해를 많이 하셨을 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 757.33,
      "end": 757.47,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 757.47,
      "end": 760.99,
      "text": "Cars, engines, nowadays, are measured in horsepower."
    },
    {
      "start": 761.21,
      "end": 761.47,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 761.91,
      "end": 762.27,
      "text": "Still."
    },
    {
      "start": 762.27,
      "end": 762.69,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 763.13,
      "end": 766.25,
      "text": "지금도 마력으로 우리가 계산을 하기도 하죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 766.73,
      "end": 768.19,
      "text": "자, 이 내용 다시 한번 들어보겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 768.19,
      "end": 774.03,
      "text": "If we cannot reach an agreement today, my company will die right here in your hotel room."
    },
    {
      "start": 774.03,
      "end": 778.22,
      "text": "But if it does perish, so might your dream of harnessing power from Niagara."
    },
    {
      "start": 779.02,
      "end": 780.78,
      "text": "So, do we have a deal?"
    },
    {
      "start": 781.5,
      "end": 782.24,
      "text": "5,000."
    },
    {
      "start": 783.07,
      "end": 783.69,
      "text": "1,000."
    },
    {
      "start": 784.23,
      "end": 787.73,
      "text": "I'll give you $2.50 per horsepower."
    },
    {
      "start": 787.73,
      "end": 793.17,
      "text": "Oh, Westinghouse Electric became more powerful because of Tesla."
    },
    {
      "start": 794.51,
      "end": 797.25,
      "text": "와, 천군만마를 얻은 그런 기분이겠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 797.43,
      "end": 797.83,
      "text": "Woohoo!"
    },
    {
      "start": 797.97,
      "end": 798.17,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 798.33,
      "end": 800.75,
      "text": "근데 이것 때문에 에디슨이 분노하게 되죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 801.01,
      "end": 801.91,
      "text": "Oh, yes, of course."
    },
    {
      "start": 802.05,
      "end": 802.17,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 802.25,
      "end": 805.57,
      "text": "그래서 본격적인 전류 전쟁이 시작이 되는 것과 마찬가지인 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 805.71,
      "end": 806.29,
      "text": "You traitor!"
    },
    {
      "start": 806.61,
      "end": 806.93,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 807.01,
      "end": 808.73,
      "text": "How dare him go to my enemy!"
    },
    {
      "start": 808.91,
      "end": 810.21,
      "text": "자기가 잘못한 걸 생각 안 하고."
    },
    {
      "start": 810.67,
      "end": 811.77,
      "text": "Yeah, come on."
    },
    {
      "start": 811.81,
      "end": 812.11,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 812.39,
      "end": 813.35,
      "text": "자, 내용 살펴볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 813.89,
      "end": 816.57,
      "text": "If we cannot reach an agreement today,"
    },
    {
      "start": 816.57,
      "end": 820.25,
      "text": "my company will die right here in your hotel room."
    },
    {
      "start": 820.37,
      "end": 822.09,
      "text": "이 절실함이 막 느껴집니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 822.15,
      "end": 824.33,
      "text": "They're standing in Tesla's hotel room."
    },
    {
      "start": 824.37,
      "end": 824.63,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 824.81,
      "end": 825.69,
      "text": "Fancy hotel room."
    },
    {
      "start": 825.75,
      "end": 825.99,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 826.25,
      "end": 827.47,
      "text": "지금 Westinghouse가"
    },
    {
      "start": 827.47,
      "end": 830.31,
      "text": "테슬라가 머물고 있는 호텔에 들어와가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 830.31,
      "end": 831.69,
      "text": "이야기하고 있는 장면인데"
    },
    {
      "start": 831.69,
      "end": 834.39,
      "text": "If we cannot reach an agreement today,"
    },
    {
      "start": 834.91,
      "end": 836.07,
      "text": "만약에 오늘 우리가"
    },
    {
      "start": 836.07,
      "end": 838.89,
      "text": "이 agreement에 도달하지 않는다면"
    },
    {
      "start": 838.89,
      "end": 839.65,
      "text": "이라는 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 840.37,
      "end": 842.01,
      "text": "오늘 우리가 합의하지 못하면"
    },
    {
      "start": 842.01,
      "end": 842.87,
      "text": "What will happen?"
    },
    {
      "start": 842.87,
      "end": 845.09,
      "text": "Oh, my company, 우리 회사는"
    },
    {
      "start": 845.09,
      "end": 848.79,
      "text": "will die right here in your hotel room."
    },
    {
      "start": 849.05,
      "end": 849.37,
      "text": "Die!"
    },
    {
      "start": 849.95,
      "end": 851.97,
      "text": "아까 저번에 배웠던 dissolve보다"
    },
    {
      "start": 851.97,
      "end": 853.23,
      "text": "더 강력한 느낌."
    },
    {
      "start": 853.49,
      "end": 855.29,
      "text": "좀 더 직접적으로 확 와닿네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 855.39,
      "end": 856.41,
      "text": "My company will die"
    },
    {
      "start": 856.41,
      "end": 858.57,
      "text": "right here in your hotel room."
    },
    {
      "start": 858.73,
      "end": 861.21,
      "text": "우리 회사는 여기에서 죽을 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 861.55,
      "end": 863.77,
      "text": "바로 여기, 당신 호텔방에서."
    },
    {
      "start": 863.87,
      "end": 864.97,
      "text": "That sounds like a threat."
    },
    {
      "start": 865.15,
      "end": 865.43,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 865.51,
      "end": 868.13,
      "text": "Like you are murdering my company"
    },
    {
      "start": 868.13,
      "end": 870.39,
      "text": "if you don't sign this agreement."
    },
    {
      "start": 870.55,
      "end": 870.83,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 870.83,
      "end": 871.91,
      "text": "If you don't agree to this."
    },
    {
      "start": 872.05,
      "end": 872.41,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 872.55,
      "end": 874.25,
      "text": "약간의 협박처럼 느껴지기도 하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 874.25,
      "end": 875.43,
      "text": "절실함도 느껴지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 875.43,
      "end": 876.25,
      "text": "어쨌든 that means"
    },
    {
      "start": 876.25,
      "end": 877.59,
      "text": "they must work together."
    },
    {
      "start": 877.71,
      "end": 877.99,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 878.27,
      "end": 879.13,
      "text": "They're both desperate."
    },
    {
      "start": 879.35,
      "end": 879.55,
      "text": "응."
    },
    {
      "start": 880.37,
      "end": 882.43,
      "text": "But if it does perish,"
    },
    {
      "start": 882.85,
      "end": 883.97,
      "text": "so might your dream"
    },
    {
      "start": 883.97,
      "end": 885.25,
      "text": "of harnessing power"
    },
    {
      "start": 885.25,
      "end": 886.29,
      "text": "from Niagara."
    },
    {
      "start": 887.61,
      "end": 889.01,
      "text": "우리 이거 들어보지 않았나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 889.11,
      "end": 890.21,
      "text": "혹시 못 들으셨나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 890.77,
      "end": 891.41,
      "text": "나이아가라."
    },
    {
      "start": 891.57,
      "end": 892.65,
      "text": "아, 나이아가라."
    },
    {
      "start": 893.05,
      "end": 893.76,
      "text": "나이아가라."
    },
    {
      "start": 893.82,
      "end": 895.16,
      "text": "그거 봉토 발음으로."
    },
    {
      "start": 895.34,
      "end": 895.5,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 895.82,
      "end": 896.54,
      "text": "나이아가라."
    },
    {
      "start": 896.66,
      "end": 897.96,
      "text": "나이가 갔으면 좋겠네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 898.28,
      "end": 898.84,
      "text": "자, 나이아가라."
    },
    {
      "start": 898.86,
      "end": 899.72,
      "text": "Have you been to Niagara?"
    },
    {
      "start": 899.72,
      "end": 900.76,
      "text": "아니요."
    },
    {
      "start": 900.84,
      "end": 901.62,
      "text": "I want to go too."
    },
    {
      "start": 902.1,
      "end": 903.06,
      "text": "I've never been."
    },
    {
      "start": 903.14,
      "end": 903.74,
      "text": "You haven't been?"
    },
    {
      "start": 903.78,
      "end": 904.58,
      "text": "나이아가라 Falls."
    },
    {
      "start": 905.02,
      "end": 906.74,
      "text": "Just because I'm from the U.S."
    },
    {
      "start": 906.82,
      "end": 908.24,
      "text": "doesn't mean I've been everywhere."
    },
    {
      "start": 909.0,
      "end": 910.76,
      "text": "하기에 우리가 서울에 산다고"
    },
    {
      "start": 910.76,
      "end": 912.78,
      "text": "다들 뭐 남산타워를 가거나"
    },
    {
      "start": 912.78,
      "end": 915.66,
      "text": "63빌딩을 100% 다 가려는 법은 없잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 915.76,
      "end": 917.58,
      "text": "Yeah, I've been more in Korea actually"
    },
    {
      "start": 917.58,
      "end": 918.42,
      "text": "than the U.S."
    },
    {
      "start": 919.02,
      "end": 919.7,
      "text": "네, 맞습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 919.76,
      "end": 920.54,
      "text": "나이아가라 한번."
    },
    {
      "start": 920.76,
      "end": 920.96,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 921.18,
      "end": 922.04,
      "text": "I want to go."
    },
    {
      "start": 922.16,
      "end": 922.32,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 922.66,
      "end": 923.9,
      "text": "어쨌든 해석해드릴게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 924.14,
      "end": 925.84,
      "text": "But if it does perish,"
    },
    {
      "start": 925.84,
      "end": 928.78,
      "text": "자, perish라는 단어가 이렇게 들렸잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 928.88,
      "end": 929.44,
      "text": "Perish."
    },
    {
      "start": 930.12,
      "end": 931.8,
      "text": "만약에 perish 하면"
    },
    {
      "start": 931.8,
      "end": 932.5,
      "text": "Die."
    },
    {
      "start": 932.7,
      "end": 934.2,
      "text": "죽다, 소멸되다."
    },
    {
      "start": 934.34,
      "end": 936.34,
      "text": "라는 또 비슷한 의미가 들렸어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 936.5,
      "end": 940.74,
      "text": "만약에 그렇게 되면, 죽게 되면, 협상이 결렬되면."
    },
    {
      "start": 941.16,
      "end": 944.08,
      "text": "So, might your dream of harnessing power from"
    },
    {
      "start": 944.08,
      "end": 945.9,
      "text": "나이아가라의 본토 발음은?"
    },
    {
      "start": 946.26,
      "end": 946.74,
      "text": "Niagara."
    },
    {
      "start": 946.74,
      "end": 946.94,
      "text": "Niagara."
    },
    {
      "start": 947.94,
      "end": 948.58,
      "text": "Niagara."
    },
    {
      "start": 948.58,
      "end": 950.52,
      "text": "보통 Niagara Falls이라고."
    },
    {
      "start": 950.84,
      "end": 951.6,
      "text": "붙여서 얘기하죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 951.76,
      "end": 952.66,
      "text": "조금 생소해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 952.72,
      "end": 953.7,
      "text": "Niagara만 얘기하니까."
    },
    {
      "start": 953.78,
      "end": 954.18,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 954.48,
      "end": 955.18,
      "text": "Niagara Falls."
    },
    {
      "start": 955.34,
      "end": 955.58,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 956.8,
      "end": 961.0,
      "text": "당신의 나이아가라 폭포로부터의"
    },
    {
      "start": 961.0,
      "end": 965.38,
      "text": "동력을 이용하겠다는 꿈도 그렇게 될 겁니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 965.92,
      "end": 966.6,
      "text": "죽게 될 거다."
    },
    {
      "start": 966.62,
      "end": 968.44,
      "text": "너의 꿈도 죽게 될 거다."
    },
    {
      "start": 968.44,
      "end": 969.74,
      "text": "So, you need me."
    },
    {
      "start": 970.04,
      "end": 971.32,
      "text": "I need you and you need me."
    },
    {
      "start": 971.32,
      "end": 971.58,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 971.94,
      "end": 973.24,
      "text": "우리는 서로 필요한 관계잖아?"
    },
    {
      "start": 973.88,
      "end": 974.96,
      "text": "라고 아주 소프트하게"
    },
    {
      "start": 974.96,
      "end": 977.42,
      "text": "threatening 하고 있는 그런 상황입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 977.52,
      "end": 978.1,
      "text": "What a businessman."
    },
    {
      "start": 978.1,
      "end": 978.66,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 979.32,
      "end": 981.78,
      "text": "So, so, do we have a deal?"
    },
    {
      "start": 982.06,
      "end": 982.18,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 982.3,
      "end": 983.4,
      "text": "계속해서 웨스팅하우스가"
    },
    {
      "start": 983.4,
      "end": 984.76,
      "text": "So, do we have a deal?"
    },
    {
      "start": 985.36,
      "end": 986.98,
      "text": "자, 그러면 거래된 건가요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 987.22,
      "end": 988.04,
      "text": "라고 질문합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 988.2,
      "end": 989.8,
      "text": "Very, very good sentence."
    },
    {
      "start": 989.96,
      "end": 990.14,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 990.3,
      "end": 991.12,
      "text": "Do we have a deal?"
    },
    {
      "start": 991.3,
      "end": 992.44,
      "text": "We have a deal."
    },
    {
      "start": 992.8,
      "end": 993.86,
      "text": "Let's make a deal."
    },
    {
      "start": 993.94,
      "end": 998.06,
      "text": "유명한 미국 TV 게임 방송, 게임 프로그램이 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 998.06,
      "end": 1003.74,
      "text": "뭔가 거래를 제안하고, 합리적인 가격에 거래하고, 성공하고 이런 내용인가요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1004.08,
      "end": 1005.16,
      "text": "I think so, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 1005.16,
      "end": 1009.26,
      "text": "So, my mom, my grandma, and my mom love this show."
    },
    {
      "start": 1009.62,
      "end": 1013.2,
      "text": "And it has something to do with money and making deals."
    },
    {
      "start": 1013.4,
      "end": 1013.58,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 1013.76,
      "end": 1014.62,
      "text": "That's all I know."
    },
    {
      "start": 1014.74,
      "end": 1015.76,
      "text": "한번 찾아봐야겠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 1015.76,
      "end": 1016.58,
      "text": "Let's make a deal."
    },
    {
      "start": 1016.58,
      "end": 1020.14,
      "text": "Five, now they're making a deal."
    },
    {
      "start": 1020.26,
      "end": 1020.4,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 1020.4,
      "end": 1021.4,
      "text": "액수 말해야죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 1021.5,
      "end": 1022.76,
      "text": "협상 들어가야죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 1023.54,
      "end": 1024.5,
      "text": "Five thousand."
    },
    {
      "start": 1026.04,
      "end": 1027.54,
      "text": "No answer."
    },
    {
      "start": 1028.26,
      "end": 1028.76,
      "text": "All right."
    },
    {
      "start": 1029.22,
      "end": 1030.18,
      "text": "One thousand."
    },
    {
      "start": 1030.38,
      "end": 1031.26,
      "text": "Oh, 그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 1031.48,
      "end": 1032.58,
      "text": "갑자기 훅 낮췄어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 1032.94,
      "end": 1033.72,
      "text": "Oh, 자신감."
    },
    {
      "start": 1033.8,
      "end": 1034.58,
      "text": "Where's his confidence?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1034.72,
      "end": 1035.1,
      "text": "그러게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 1035.34,
      "end": 1036.32,
      "text": "테슬라가 하는 말이,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1036.58,
      "end": 1037.12,
      "text": "오천 달러?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1037.58,
      "end": 1038.06,
      "text": "그랬는데,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1038.72,
      "end": 1040.18,
      "text": "웨스팅하우스가 잠잠하니까,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1040.48,
      "end": 1041.02,
      "text": "All right."
    },
    {
      "start": 1041.2,
      "end": 1041.78,
      "text": "One thousand."
    },
    {
      "start": 1042.0,
      "end": 1043.26,
      "text": "이렇게 확 내렸습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 1043.3,
      "end": 1044.5,
      "text": "액수수로 낮췄어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 1045.08,
      "end": 1045.98,
      "text": "말도 없었는데."
    },
    {
      "start": 1047.04,
      "end": 1047.86,
      "text": "Poor guy."
    },
    {
      "start": 1047.86,
      "end": 1049.46,
      "text": "He's lost his confidence."
    },
    {
      "start": 1050.89,
      "end": 1052.79,
      "text": "I'll give you two fifty."
    },
    {
      "start": 1053.13,
      "end": 1054.77,
      "text": "Two dollars and fifty cents."
    },
    {
      "start": 1055.21,
      "end": 1056.85,
      "text": "저요까지도 그거 되게 깜짝 놀랐잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 1056.97,
      "end": 1057.17,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1057.51,
      "end": 1058.11,
      "text": "Two fifty?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1058.71,
      "end": 1060.93,
      "text": "That's a lot less than one thousand."
    },
    {
      "start": 1061.99,
      "end": 1063.55,
      "text": "Per horsepower."
    },
    {
      "start": 1065.13,
      "end": 1067.35,
      "text": "This is the important line."
    },
    {
      "start": 1067.49,
      "end": 1068.41,
      "text": "Per horsepower."
    },
    {
      "start": 1068.63,
      "end": 1071.03,
      "text": "웨스팅하우스가 제안하는 금액은 얼마냐면,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1071.27,
      "end": 1073.63,
      "text": "I'll give you two point five,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1073.85,
      "end": 1075.75,
      "text": "fifty dollars이잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 1075.79,
      "end": 1077.53,
      "text": "Yeah, two dollars and fifty cents."
    },
    {
      "start": 1077.53,
      "end": 1079.55,
      "text": "Yeah, two dollars and fifty cents."
    },
    {
      "start": 1079.69,
      "end": 1082.27,
      "text": "이렇게 달러스가 들렸는데,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1082.81,
      "end": 1085.31,
      "text": "2.5달러 들이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 1086.01,
      "end": 1087.33,
      "text": "그래서 되게 충격적이었는데,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1087.39,
      "end": 1087.53,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1087.95,
      "end": 1090.31,
      "text": "Per horse power이라고 했잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 1090.51,
      "end": 1092.03,
      "text": "1 마력당이라고 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 1092.39,
      "end": 1093.67,
      "text": "I don't know exactly,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1093.85,
      "end": 1094.97,
      "text": "but I think it's a lot of money."
    },
    {
      "start": 1095.15,
      "end": 1097.71,
      "text": "Yeah, his motor apparently has a lot of,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1097.77,
      "end": 1098.81,
      "text": "needs a lot of horsepower."
    },
    {
      "start": 1099.07,
      "end": 1099.29,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 1099.55,
      "end": 1101.59,
      "text": "So it's going to be over a million dollars."
    },
    {
      "start": 1101.93,
      "end": 1102.89,
      "text": "Oh, amazing."
    },
    {
      "start": 1103.17,
      "end": 1104.41,
      "text": "That's a fortune."
    },
    {
      "start": 1104.59,
      "end": 1104.91,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 1104.91,
      "end": 1105.87,
      "text": "A big fortune."
    },
    {
      "start": 1105.87,
      "end": 1107.31,
      "text": "진짜 대박났네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 1107.79,
      "end": 1109.79,
      "text": "자, 마지막으로 이 내용 한 번 더 들어볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 1109.79,
      "end": 1112.67,
      "text": "If we cannot reach an agreement today,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1112.77,
      "end": 1115.59,
      "text": "my company will die right here in your hotel room."
    },
    {
      "start": 1116.26,
      "end": 1117.2,
      "text": "But if it does perish,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1117.3,
      "end": 1119.76,
      "text": "so might your dream of harnessing power from Niagara."
    },
    {
      "start": 1120.56,
      "end": 1122.32,
      "text": "So, do we have a deal?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1123.02,
      "end": 1123.72,
      "text": "Five thousand."
    },
    {
      "start": 1124.64,
      "end": 1125.2,
      "text": "One thousand."
    },
    {
      "start": 1125.2,
      "end": 1127.76,
      "text": "I'll give you two dollars and fifty cents"
    },
    {
      "start": 1127.76,
      "end": 1129.4,
      "text": "per horse power."
    },
    {
      "start": 1130.34,
      "end": 1136.72,
      "text": "네, 영화가 흘러갈수록 점차 이 에디슨과 테슬라의 치열한 경쟁이,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1137.06,
      "end": 1139.22,
      "text": "전쟁이 더해질 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 1139.48,
      "end": 1140.18,
      "text": "Who's going to win?"
    },
